# Choice Properties — Cursor Rules
# Loaded automatically by Cursor IDE on project open.
# Full rule set: p2/.agents/instructions.md

This is a STATIC WEBSITE. Read .agents/instructions.md before taking any action.

## Critical Rules (Short Version)

- DO NOT run npm install — no runtime dependencies exist
- DO NOT start any server or dev server
- DO NOT create config.js — it is generated by Cloudflare at build time
- DO NOT connect to any local database (ignore DATABASE_URL, PGHOST, etc.)
- DO NOT modify: generate-config.js, _headers, SETUP.sql, js/cp-api.js, js/apply*.js

## Only Permitted Actions

- Edit static HTML, CSS, and frontend JS files
- Edit Supabase Edge Functions (supabase/functions/ — Deno TypeScript)
- Push to GitHub — Cloudflare Pages auto-deploys on push to main

## Deployment Flow

Replit (edit) → GitHub (push) → Cloudflare Pages (auto-deploy) → Live site

No other path is valid.
